          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1581515898732-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put your<strong> ciabatta[s]</strong> in the oven for 3-4 min or until crusty and warmed through</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1581515904060-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1581515904060-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1581515904060-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1581515904060-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1581515904060-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms have caramelised, reduce the heat to medium and add your<strong> soy sauce</strong> and <strong>agave</strong> to the pan</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min further, turning the mushrooms to coat them fully in the sauce – these are your <strong>sticky mushrooms</strong></p><p>Carefully cut the<strong> warmed ciabatta[s] </strong>in half</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1581515909311-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1581515909311-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1581515909311-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1581515909311-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1581515909311-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Spread each<strong> ciabatta</strong> with some<strong> spicy mayo</strong>, then top with the<strong> sticky mushrooms</strong>, a handful of <strong>zingy veg</strong>, the <strong>chopped coriander</strong> and some<strong> sliced chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) – this is your <strong>mushroom bánh mì</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> mushroom bánh mì</strong> with the<strong> chips</strong> and <strong>remaining zingy veg</strong> to the side and garnish with any<strong> remaining chopped coriander</strong> and <strong>sliced chilli</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
